  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Some magic items take damage over the course of an adventure. It costs no more to repair a magic item with the Craft skill than it does to repair its nonmagical counterpart. The make whole spell also repairs a damaged--but not completely broken--magic item.",
